data.description: Welcome to 2503 91st Street, a spacious& versatile family home that offers three levels of comfortable living space. Updates incl: NEW Upper Appliances(2023),NEW SIDING(2022), NEW Roof (2022), NEW Windows on 2nd flr & 1/2 of main(2022),NEW lwr appliances(2019),& Furnace (2016)3 kitchens! The lower level of this residence is uniquely equipped to serve as a self-contained living space, perfect accommodating extended family or guests! Conveniently Located near schools, shops and restaurants! Perfect for IL commuter!! So much SPACE!
